content: Sanjeev Setia's Home Page Sanjeev Setia Professor Department of Computer Science George Mason University Contact Info: Email: setia at gmu dot edu US mail: Department of Computer Science George Mason University 4400 University Drive Fairfax, VA 22030-4444 On foot: Room 5305, Engineering Building Office Hours:  Mon 11AM - 12PM Biosketch Honors/Recognition Co-authored journal article (LEAP+....) included in Google Scholar’s list of classic papers in the area of Computer Networks & Wireless Communication Listed at #28 in AMiner.org’s Most Influential Scholar list in the area of Security (2016) Research Interests: GPU Cluster Scheduling, Wireless Networks, Security of Sensor Networks and MANETs, Distributed Systems Publications (Google Scholar) Students Teaching CS 475 (Concurrent & Distributed Systems)
